1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:01:00,000
(Watch on www.kisskh.li Support Admin)

2
00:01:30,940 --> 00:01:33,948
[Episode 6]

3
00:01:33,948 --> 00:01:37,063
[He Family Clinic]

4
00:01:43,799 --> 00:01:46,480
His mother died because of the triads.

5
00:01:53,400 --> 00:01:55,319
It's said that just before she died,

6
00:01:55,319 --> 00:01:57,079
her last words were...

7
00:01:57,079 --> 00:02:01,200
"Never let He Chu San
get involved with the triads."

8
00:02:04,040 --> 00:02:05,120
Dad.

9
00:02:05,120 --> 00:02:07,280
Dad, hold on a little longer.

10
00:02:11,319 --> 00:02:12,800
Dad, just hang in there a bit longer.

11
00:02:12,800 --> 00:02:13,800
What happened?

12
00:02:13,800 --> 00:02:15,719
Get in the car. Come on.

13
00:02:16,680 --> 00:02:18,280
- Dad.
- Doctor!

14
00:02:18,280 --> 00:02:19,759
- Emergency! Doctor!
- Where is the emergency room?

15
00:02:19,759 --> 00:02:22,319
- Emergency.
- Come in, what's the patient's condition?

16
00:02:22,319 --> 00:02:24,360
- Prepare for surgery immediately.
- Dad.

17
00:02:25,000 --> 00:02:28,119
Dad.

18
00:02:30,000 --> 00:02:31,840
- Dad.
- The family waits outside.

19
00:02:31,840 --> 00:02:33,160
Please wait outside.

20
00:02:34,360 --> 00:02:35,640
Wait here.

21
00:02:40,680 --> 00:02:42,719
Excuse me.

22
00:02:42,719 --> 00:02:44,039
It hurts so much.

23
00:02:44,039 --> 00:02:45,480
- Hurry.
- Okay.

24
00:02:59,319 --> 00:03:00,480
Thank you.

25
00:03:42,120 --> 00:03:43,559
It's okay.

26
00:03:45,360 --> 00:03:47,519
When I got home,

27
00:03:48,680 --> 00:03:51,759
I found him already lying on the ground.

28
00:03:51,759 --> 00:03:54,400
I couldn't wake him no matter how I called him.

29
00:03:54,400 --> 00:03:56,760
The shop door was open at that time.

30
00:03:58,000 --> 00:04:00,639
But the neighbors were all asleep.

31
00:04:00,639 --> 00:04:02,760
No one noticed him.

32
00:04:05,120 --> 00:04:06,759
Don't worry.

33
00:04:06,759 --> 00:04:08,080
It's okay.

34
00:04:16,399 --> 00:04:19,360
He supported me by working since I was little.

35
00:04:19,360 --> 00:04:20,999
He took care of me.

36
00:04:22,360 --> 00:04:24,480
I just hoped to get into a good university

37
00:04:24,480 --> 00:04:26,199
and find a good job.

38
00:04:27,839 --> 00:04:30,800
Then I can take him away
from Ganglong Walled City.

39
00:04:32,079 --> 00:04:34,480
All of this was about to come true.

40
00:04:34,480 --> 00:04:37,319
But now he's in trouble.

41
00:04:38,959 --> 00:04:40,679
I'm useless.

42
00:04:41,399 --> 00:04:44,000
- I'm so useless.
- It's okay.

43
00:04:44,000 --> 00:04:45,319
Don't worry.

44
00:04:46,079 --> 00:04:47,920
It's okay.

45
00:04:47,920 --> 00:04:49,560
It's fine.

46
00:04:49,560 --> 00:04:51,439
Liu Yi.

47
00:04:53,639 --> 00:04:54,879
It's okay.

48
00:04:56,160 --> 00:04:57,679
Don't worry.

49
00:05:00,480 --> 00:05:02,280
You've done great.

50
00:05:35,240 --> 00:05:36,720
How is he, doctor?

51
00:05:36,720 --> 00:05:38,000
Fortunately, he was brought in in time.

52
00:05:38,000 --> 00:05:39,360
The surgery was very successful.

53
00:05:39,360 --> 00:05:40,519
Once the patient wakes up,

54
00:05:40,519 --> 00:05:41,800
he'll be moved to a regular ward.

55
00:05:41,800 --> 00:05:43,800
Family members can visit then.

56
00:05:43,800 --> 00:05:45,360
- Thank you, doctor.
- Thank you.

57
00:05:45,360 --> 00:05:47,199
You're welcome. It's my duty.

58
00:05:58,800 --> 00:06:01,399
By the way, are you hungry?

59
00:06:01,399 --> 00:06:03,559
- I'll go buy breakfast.
- Xia Liu Yi.

60
00:06:07,240 --> 00:06:09,199
Thank you.

61
00:06:09,199 --> 00:06:11,680
If you hadn't shown up in time,

62
00:06:11,680 --> 00:06:14,160
it might have been too late.

63
00:06:15,120 --> 00:06:16,600
What are you saying?

64
00:06:17,319 --> 00:06:20,679
Mr. He is a good person,
so the heavens will protect him.

65
00:06:26,279 --> 00:06:28,480
I-I'm sorry.

66
00:06:29,920 --> 00:06:32,639
I made you angry yesterday.

67
00:06:39,959 --> 00:06:41,480
But...

68
00:06:42,600 --> 00:06:44,800
I really can't get involved with the gang.

69
00:06:48,680 --> 00:06:51,480
The person who should apologize is me.

70
00:06:51,480 --> 00:06:52,800
Not you.

71
00:07:00,720 --> 00:07:03,040
Cui Dong Dong told me.

72
00:07:03,040 --> 00:07:04,960
Mr. He isn't your father.

73
00:07:07,040 --> 00:07:09,079
I didn't know before.

74
00:07:09,079 --> 00:07:10,720
I even forced you to join the gang.

75
00:07:12,560 --> 00:07:14,920
I forced you to do things
you didn't want to do.

76
00:07:16,519 --> 00:07:19,560
I thought you didn't want to join the gang

77
00:07:19,560 --> 00:07:21,519
because you were scared of dying,

78
00:07:21,519 --> 00:07:23,600
because you looked down on us.

79
00:07:26,680 --> 00:07:28,480
I also owe an apology to Mr. He.

80
00:07:29,519 --> 00:07:32,439
He saved me, and yet I treated you like this.

81
00:07:33,120 --> 00:07:34,480
Don't worry.

82
00:07:34,480 --> 00:07:35,960
I won't do it anymore.

83
00:07:38,240 --> 00:07:40,679
What exactly do you want to say?

84
00:07:45,319 --> 00:07:46,840
If...

85
00:07:47,800 --> 00:07:49,960
If you really don't like the gang,

86
00:07:52,040 --> 00:07:55,639
I will avoid appearing before you and Mr. He.

87
00:07:55,639 --> 00:07:56,920
That's not it.

88
00:08:18,079 --> 00:08:20,480
I don't think my parents were dragged into this

89
00:08:20,480 --> 00:08:22,559
because of the gang.

90
00:08:25,319 --> 00:08:27,879
It just happened that the person my mom liked

91
00:08:28,759 --> 00:08:30,360
was from the gang.

92
00:08:33,020 --> 00:08:36,919
I also know that many people join the gang

93
00:08:36,919 --> 00:08:38,839
because they can't survive otherwise.

94
00:08:40,960 --> 00:08:44,439
But not all gang members are bad people.

95
00:08:45,559 --> 00:08:46,839
Like you.

96
00:08:52,480 --> 00:08:56,040
I'm also living a happy life now.

97
00:08:56,679 --> 00:08:58,679
Dad has given me so much love.

98
00:09:00,360 --> 00:09:03,000
It's just that he got sick this time.

99
00:09:03,000 --> 00:09:07,240
That's when I suddenly realized
my concern for him

100
00:09:07,240 --> 00:09:09,599
was nowhere near as much as his worry for me.

101
00:09:12,559 --> 00:09:14,280
Fortunately, he's okay.

102
00:09:15,399 --> 00:09:17,800
Otherwise, I really wouldn't know what to do.

103
00:09:23,000 --> 00:09:24,319
It's fine.

104
00:09:25,600 --> 00:09:28,280
In the future, I will help you
take care of Mr. He.

105
00:09:29,279 --> 00:09:30,600
Is the family of He Guang Sheng here?

106
00:09:30,600 --> 00:09:31,679
I am.

107
00:09:31,679 --> 00:09:32,919
Here.

108
00:09:32,919 --> 00:09:34,080
Pick up the medication.

109
00:09:34,080 --> 00:09:35,520
You wait here for me.

110
00:09:51,480 --> 00:09:52,760
Mr. Hua.

111
00:09:53,639 --> 00:09:55,000
Let me do it.

112
00:09:56,200 --> 00:09:57,360
Madam Hua.

113
00:09:57,360 --> 00:09:59,559
- You're back.
- Madam Hua.

114
00:09:59,559 --> 00:10:01,559
Let me do it. I'll help Dad.

115
00:10:01,559 --> 00:10:04,480
No need. Hold the bag.

116
00:10:04,480 --> 00:10:06,000
Take it easy.

117
00:10:06,000 --> 00:10:07,159
You don't need to help me.

118
00:10:07,159 --> 00:10:08,880
I'm fine now.

119
00:10:11,000 --> 00:10:13,360
- Dad.
- You two rascals.

120
00:10:13,360 --> 00:10:15,639
You don't need to help me.

121
00:10:15,639 --> 00:10:16,840
Watch the stairs.

122
00:10:16,840 --> 00:10:18,559
Sheng, you're finally back.

123
00:10:18,559 --> 00:10:19,639
Hurry up, come and eat.

124
00:10:19,639 --> 00:10:20,919
You prepared so much.

125
00:10:20,919 --> 00:10:22,159
I didn't prepare this.

126
00:10:22,159 --> 00:10:23,959
It's...

127
00:10:24,600 --> 00:10:26,880
Mr. He, what do you think?

128
00:10:29,679 --> 00:10:32,279
- A television!
- Yes.

129
00:10:32,279 --> 00:10:34,799
This won't do. It's very expensive.

130
00:10:34,799 --> 00:10:36,280
Be careful.

131
00:10:38,679 --> 00:10:41,599
You're amazing. Thank you so much.

132
00:10:44,799 --> 00:10:46,120
Well?

133
00:10:46,120 --> 00:10:48,480
I told you I'd help take care of Mr. He.

134
00:10:48,480 --> 00:10:49,920
I didn't lie to you.

135
00:10:57,360 --> 00:10:58,640
Let me do it.

136
00:11:05,240 --> 00:11:07,600
Dad, let's eat.

137
00:11:07,600 --> 00:11:10,360
Come on, let's eat.

138
00:11:10,360 --> 00:11:11,760
Come on, eat.

139
00:11:14,000 --> 00:11:16,399
Come on, sit down.

140
00:11:16,399 --> 00:11:17,679
Come on.

141
00:11:19,120 --> 00:11:22,039
- Sit down.
- You're really good.

142
00:11:22,039 --> 00:11:24,600
Come on, sit down.

143
00:11:24,600 --> 00:11:26,679
- Come on.
- Why so much?

144
00:11:27,960 --> 00:11:28,960
Let's drink first.

145
00:11:28,960 --> 00:11:30,640
Do you like it?

146
00:11:39,519 --> 00:11:41,200
Xu Ying met Fei Qi before he died.

147
00:11:41,200 --> 00:11:44,080
Fei Qi was unhappy about Qing Long
opening a nightclub on his turf.

148
00:11:44,080 --> 00:11:45,247
The two of them...

149
00:11:45,247 --> 00:11:48,360
I knew about their collusion a long time ago.

150
00:11:48,360 --> 00:11:51,240
Fei Qi and Hesheng gang
will be taken down by me.

151
00:11:51,240 --> 00:11:53,480
Speak about things I don't know.

152
00:11:53,480 --> 00:11:56,399
Xu Ying's two trusted subordinates
seem to owe money.

153
00:11:56,399 --> 00:11:58,120
Their homes are being stripped
because of debts.

154
00:11:58,120 --> 00:12:00,480
Their wives and children
have fled to their hometowns.

155
00:12:00,480 --> 00:12:02,279
But I don't know
if they really went back home or...

156
00:12:02,279 --> 00:12:06,519
I remember someone named Zheng,
who followed Xu Ying for a long time.

157
00:12:06,519 --> 00:12:07,880
He's from Caodong.

158
00:12:09,000 --> 00:12:12,000
Here's the deal. You go to Caodong
and check things out.

159
00:12:12,000 --> 00:12:13,720
See if they are still alive.

160
00:12:13,720 --> 00:12:15,320
Let me know right away.

161
00:12:15,320 --> 00:12:16,559
The reward is doubled.

162
00:12:25,919 --> 00:12:27,199
Goodbye.

163
00:12:35,519 --> 00:12:37,759
We'll leave first.

164
00:12:37,759 --> 00:12:38,920
Bye-bye.

165
00:12:40,080 --> 00:12:42,319
Liu Yi, what are you doing here?

166
00:12:43,279 --> 00:12:44,439
Get in.

167
00:12:53,919 --> 00:12:55,280
Where are we going?

168
00:13:26,159 --> 00:13:27,160
Are you kidding me?

169
00:13:27,160 --> 00:13:28,199
I haven't even arrived yet.

170
00:13:28,199 --> 00:13:29,320
But you guys are already drinking?

171
00:13:29,320 --> 00:13:34,599
Who knew that you'd dress up
to chase girls all morning?

172
00:13:37,039 --> 00:13:38,480
Isn't this the top student

173
00:13:38,480 --> 00:13:41,399
our boss has been thinking about?

174
00:13:41,399 --> 00:13:43,000
He Chu San.

175
00:13:44,279 --> 00:13:49,959
Everyone, this is a financial industry elite.

176
00:13:50,759 --> 00:13:52,040
Here!

177
00:13:53,240 --> 00:13:54,240
Have a drink.

178
00:13:54,240 --> 00:13:55,400
Come on.

179
00:13:56,159 --> 00:13:57,799
I'll drink first as a toast.

180
00:13:57,799 --> 00:13:59,360
Getting bold after a few drinks, huh?

181
00:13:59,360 --> 00:14:01,200
You start talking nonsense after a few drinks.

182
00:14:01,200 --> 00:14:02,799
Why bully a college student?

183
00:14:02,799 --> 00:14:03,919
If you dare, drink with me.

184
00:14:03,919 --> 00:14:05,719
- Come on.
- Bring it on.

185
00:14:07,080 --> 00:14:08,919
Cui Dong Dong, drink!

186
00:14:08,919 --> 00:14:10,960
Tonight, I'm going to
drink you under the table!

187
00:14:10,960 --> 00:14:12,480
I'll drink with you.

188
00:14:12,480 --> 00:14:13,720
- Come on.
- Student, join in.

189
00:14:13,720 --> 00:14:15,320
He doesn't drink, come on.

190
00:14:15,320 --> 00:14:17,760
I'll drink, come on.

191
00:14:20,279 --> 00:14:24,000
You still have the strength
to shield others from drinking,

192
00:14:24,000 --> 00:14:29,160
which means we haven't treated him well enough.

193
00:14:30,399 --> 00:14:33,719
Each of us will drink three more cups with him.

194
00:14:34,960 --> 00:14:38,760
Knock him over
before we go tease the top student.

195
00:14:41,159 --> 00:14:42,360
Drink!

196
00:14:42,360 --> 00:14:43,599
- Drink!
- Drink!

197
00:14:43,599 --> 00:14:44,639
Come on, drink!

198
00:14:44,639 --> 00:14:45,639
Come on, Boss!

199
00:14:45,639 --> 00:14:46,759
- Boss!
- Drink!

200
00:14:46,759 --> 00:14:47,959
Cheers!

201
00:14:57,240 --> 00:14:59,439
Boss, keep drinking!

202
00:15:35,840 --> 00:15:37,559
Aren't you their boss?

203
00:15:37,559 --> 00:15:39,280
Why are they forcing you to drink?

204
00:15:44,679 --> 00:15:47,039
Tonight, we're all on the same team.

205
00:15:47,039 --> 00:15:49,160
Forget about boss or not.

206
00:15:50,360 --> 00:15:51,880
Listen up.

207
00:15:53,840 --> 00:15:56,719
If anything happens to you in the future,

208
00:15:57,399 --> 00:15:58,959
and I'm not around,

209
00:16:01,080 --> 00:16:04,199
you can rely on these people here today.

210
00:16:06,080 --> 00:16:08,720
I brought you here today

211
00:16:08,720 --> 00:16:11,640
to show them that you are one of us.

212
00:16:14,720 --> 00:16:18,839
I'm not part of the gang,
so what could go wrong?

213
00:16:25,879 --> 00:16:27,559
True.

214
00:16:28,320 --> 00:16:30,800
You're so obedient and smart.

215
00:16:34,039 --> 00:16:37,079
Like a fox in sheep's clothing.

216
00:16:39,600 --> 00:16:41,399
You...

217
00:16:41,399 --> 00:16:43,679
What could possibly happen to you?

218
00:16:51,120 --> 00:16:52,559
Xia Liu Yi!

219
00:16:52,559 --> 00:16:54,639
Come out here right now!

220
00:16:54,639 --> 00:16:57,679
Having fun in there with that college student?

221
00:16:59,759 --> 00:17:00,919
Cui Dong Dong!

222
00:17:00,919 --> 00:17:02,399
Could you keep your mouth shut for once?

223
00:17:02,399 --> 00:17:04,799
- Tonight, I'll poison you.
- Keep drinking!

224
00:17:04,799 --> 00:17:06,880
Later, I'll get that student dead drunk.

225
00:17:06,880 --> 00:17:08,799
Don't come out.

226
00:17:08,799 --> 00:17:10,399
They'll force you to drink.

227
00:17:11,000 --> 00:17:12,608
I already told you, Cui Dong Dong!

228
00:17:12,608 --> 00:17:14,200
He can't drink.

229
00:17:14,200 --> 00:17:16,480
Come on, we'll drink with you! Keep going!

230
00:17:16,480 --> 00:17:17,960
I'll drink with you.

231
00:17:17,960 --> 00:17:19,319
I'll drink with you!

232
00:17:19,319 --> 00:17:20,680
Drink, drink!

233
00:17:23,759 --> 00:17:29,839
He said June 1st is Children's Day.

234
00:17:29,839 --> 00:17:33,040
It's a holiday for me and my sister.

235
00:17:36,880 --> 00:17:39,319
So, today is his birthday.

236
00:18:44,039 --> 00:18:45,879
Who told you to come out?

237
00:18:50,400 --> 00:18:51,639
Xia Liu Yi.

238
00:18:52,640 --> 00:18:54,639
Your cigarette butt is about to burn your hand.

239
00:18:57,640 --> 00:18:59,319
Everyone's drunk.

240
00:19:04,920 --> 00:19:08,079
Seems like Cui Dong Dong isn't here.

241
00:19:10,640 --> 00:19:13,559
That scumbag Cui Dong Dong ran off again.

242
00:19:15,720 --> 00:19:18,040
I'm telling you...

243
00:19:19,480 --> 00:19:21,480
That scumbag Cui Dong Dong

244
00:19:21,480 --> 00:19:24,119
can drink more than anyone else

245
00:19:24,119 --> 00:19:27,759
and run away faster than anyone else.

246
00:19:27,759 --> 00:19:29,200
Scumbag.

247
00:19:30,359 --> 00:19:32,960
A bunch of useless people.

248
00:19:32,960 --> 00:19:35,079
If someone comes knocking now,

249
00:19:35,079 --> 00:19:37,720
I'd definitely be wiped out.

250
00:19:37,720 --> 00:19:39,480
Celebrating my birthday?

251
00:19:39,480 --> 00:19:41,640
It's basically my death anniversary.

252
00:19:41,640 --> 00:19:43,919
I'm all alone.

253
00:19:44,559 --> 00:19:46,200
I don't even have a birthday gift.

254
00:19:46,200 --> 00:19:48,680
Not even anyone to burn incense
at my grave next year.

255
00:20:14,319 --> 00:20:17,680
Hey, don't say that.

256
00:20:18,680 --> 00:20:20,440
Don't say that.

257
00:20:22,359 --> 00:20:24,720
I've prepared a gift for you.

258
00:20:40,240 --> 00:20:41,480
A gift?

259
00:20:49,039 --> 00:20:50,919
Show it to me.

260
00:20:57,119 --> 00:20:59,519
I didn't know today was your birthday.

261
00:20:59,519 --> 00:21:01,839
So, I didn't prepare in advance.

262
00:21:03,839 --> 00:21:05,280
I just drew it.

263
00:21:07,960 --> 00:21:09,440
Don't dislike it.

264
00:22:01,680 --> 00:22:03,079
He Chu San.

265
00:22:06,480 --> 00:22:08,280
Come with me to a place.

266
00:22:15,480 --> 00:22:16,680
Sure.

267
00:22:32,160 --> 00:22:33,680
Are you kidding me?

268
00:22:33,680 --> 00:22:35,559
Why is your driving so bad?

269
00:22:35,559 --> 00:22:38,119
I should've driven.

270
00:22:38,119 --> 00:22:40,880
I've only driven at the driving school.

271
00:22:40,880 --> 00:22:42,480
But you're drunk.

272
00:22:42,480 --> 00:22:45,520
If I let you drive, it would be like murder.

273
00:22:58,160 --> 00:22:59,359
Don't move.

274
00:23:00,279 --> 00:23:01,639
I'll go by myself.

275
00:24:09,240 --> 00:24:10,640
Bro.

276
00:24:10,640 --> 00:24:11,919
Sis.

277
00:24:13,839 --> 00:24:15,399
I'm here to visit you.

278
00:24:19,720 --> 00:24:21,000
Big Bro.

279
00:24:22,720 --> 00:24:24,480
I didn't expect this.

280
00:24:27,279 --> 00:24:29,680
I actually became the gang leader.

281
00:24:34,319 --> 00:24:36,319
The gang's affairs...

282
00:24:37,599 --> 00:24:39,720
Everything's been smooth sailing.

283
00:24:41,759 --> 00:24:43,119
It's pretty good.

284
00:24:47,680 --> 00:24:49,159
I'm doing fine, too.

285
00:24:59,240 --> 00:25:01,079
Recently, I...

286
00:25:01,079 --> 00:25:03,000
I met a new friend.

287
00:25:07,559 --> 00:25:09,079
Surprising, right?

288
00:25:11,960 --> 00:25:13,879
Not a brother.

289
00:25:14,559 --> 00:25:16,280
Not a lackey.

290
00:25:17,960 --> 00:25:19,480
Just a friend.

291
00:25:21,240 --> 00:25:22,960
It's the...

292
00:25:22,960 --> 00:25:24,960
drama-loving scholar.

293
00:25:26,200 --> 00:25:27,520
He Chu San.

294
00:25:33,880 --> 00:25:35,280
Sis.

295
00:25:37,240 --> 00:25:39,200
You said you liked him.

296
00:25:39,920 --> 00:25:41,599
You thought he was honest.

297
00:25:44,279 --> 00:25:47,200
But he's actually quite crafty.

298
00:25:48,400 --> 00:25:50,720
But he's still a loyal person.

299
00:25:52,880 --> 00:25:55,000
His family is also very nice.

300
00:26:14,759 --> 00:26:17,399
When I'm with them,

301
00:26:18,480 --> 00:26:20,039
I always think about

302
00:26:20,039 --> 00:26:22,280
the days when you were still around.

303
00:26:23,319 --> 00:26:27,680
Every time my birthday came,
you were always there.

304
00:26:29,559 --> 00:26:32,280
You would always buy a cake for me.

305
00:26:36,079 --> 00:26:37,680
This year...

306
00:26:39,200 --> 00:26:41,839
is the first time you're not
with me on my birthday.

307
00:26:48,000 --> 00:26:49,639
After that day,

308
00:26:53,559 --> 00:26:56,920
you've never come into my dreams again.

309
00:26:56,920 --> 00:26:59,359
Are you blaming me?

310
00:27:00,680 --> 00:27:03,040
Blaming me for only visiting you now?

311
00:27:10,680 --> 00:27:12,519
You...

312
00:27:12,519 --> 00:27:14,520
You're not here anymore.

313
00:27:15,279 --> 00:27:17,280
You were killed.

314
00:27:19,319 --> 00:27:21,599
It's my fault I couldn't protect you.

315
00:27:43,400 --> 00:27:44,680
Xia Liu Yi.

316
00:29:31,720 --> 00:29:33,359
Xia Liu Yi.

317
00:29:33,359 --> 00:29:35,040
I can't be your lackey.

318
00:29:35,720 --> 00:29:39,599
Because if I do,
you'll always see me as just a lackey.

319
00:30:50,480 --> 00:30:52,319
We've arrived. Go on.

320
00:30:54,239 --> 00:30:55,240
Are you kidding me?

321
00:30:55,240 --> 00:30:56,240
I can only drive at 50?

322
00:30:56,240 --> 00:30:58,480
Might as well walk.

323
00:30:58,480 --> 00:30:59,960
It's the traffic rules.

324
00:30:59,960 --> 00:31:01,720
The speed limit is 50.

325
00:31:02,519 --> 00:31:04,839
What if we get caught by the cops?

326
00:31:04,839 --> 00:31:06,280
And...

327
00:31:08,039 --> 00:31:10,799
you were drunk last night.

328
00:31:10,799 --> 00:31:12,480
All right, stop nagging.

329
00:31:12,480 --> 00:31:13,639
Get going.

330
00:31:25,480 --> 00:31:28,559
By the way, Dad said
you need acupuncture next week.

331
00:31:28,559 --> 00:31:30,079
Remember to come on time.

332
00:31:35,160 --> 00:31:36,680
He Chu San.

333
00:31:36,680 --> 00:31:39,359
Do you believe I'll twist
your head off and use it as a ball?

334
00:31:40,200 --> 00:31:41,399
Bye.

335
00:33:16,119 --> 00:33:17,879
He Chu San.

336
00:33:18,680 --> 00:33:20,960
What was he doing back then?

337
00:33:43,480 --> 00:33:44,480
Mr. He!
[Xiaoqi Trading]

338
00:33:44,480 --> 00:33:46,240
Are you here to see the boss again today?

339
00:33:46,240 --> 00:33:47,480
Yes.

340
00:33:47,480 --> 00:33:48,880
You might not see him today.

341
00:33:48,880 --> 00:33:51,480
Boss left early this morning with Dong Dong.

342
00:33:53,799 --> 00:33:55,119
He's not here?

343
00:33:55,119 --> 00:33:58,280
Yeah. Come back next time.

344
00:34:01,319 --> 00:34:02,480
All right.

345
00:34:02,480 --> 00:34:04,480
Then please pass this to him for me.

346
00:34:04,480 --> 00:34:05,520
Okay.

347
00:34:19,519 --> 00:34:21,239
Boss, Mr. He has left.

348
00:34:21,239 --> 00:34:23,479
He asked me to pass this cake to you.

349
00:34:27,840 --> 00:34:29,359
Don't touch it.

350
00:34:31,199 --> 00:34:32,280
What else did he say?

351
00:34:32,280 --> 00:34:34,480
Mr. He also said you should smoke less.

352
00:34:34,480 --> 00:34:36,220
Change your cigarettes to lollipops.

353
00:34:36,220 --> 00:34:37,840
What nonsense.

354
00:34:37,840 --> 00:34:38,840
Go away.

355
00:34:38,840 --> 00:34:40,760
Don't nag at our boss for smoking.

356
00:34:40,760 --> 00:34:42,400
A lackey who won't even kneel to the boss.

357
00:34:42,400 --> 00:34:45,280
Does he think he's the lady boss?

358
00:34:45,280 --> 00:34:46,320
Ma Ying Long.

359
00:34:46,320 --> 00:34:47,800
What did you say?

360
00:34:47,800 --> 00:34:49,239
Get out.

361
00:34:49,239 --> 00:34:50,519
Go!

362
00:34:51,280 --> 00:34:52,920
Laugh? What's so funny?

363
00:34:52,920 --> 00:34:54,399
Are you so bored?

364
00:35:00,079 --> 00:35:02,280
It looks delicious.

365
00:35:03,559 --> 00:35:04,839
I'll beat you.

366
00:35:08,840 --> 00:35:10,159
What's going on?

367
00:35:10,159 --> 00:35:12,400
The boss was out with that student, right?

368
00:35:12,400 --> 00:35:14,039
Weren't they inseparable?

369
00:35:14,039 --> 00:35:17,679
Did he find out that kid's not a good person?

370
00:35:17,679 --> 00:35:19,639
No, no.

371
00:35:19,639 --> 00:35:22,039
Something must have happened

372
00:35:22,039 --> 00:35:23,480
to change the boss like this.

373
00:35:23,480 --> 00:35:25,719
Something interesting.

374
00:35:25,719 --> 00:35:27,760
What happened?

375
00:35:27,760 --> 00:35:32,519
You said you loved the wrong person!

376
00:35:32,519 --> 00:35:36,607
Your heart is full of scars!

377
00:35:40,960 --> 00:35:42,720
What does that mean?

378
00:35:59,680 --> 00:36:00,719
Dad.

379
00:36:00,719 --> 00:36:02,519
Today, Xia Liu Yi is going for acupuncture.

380
00:36:02,519 --> 00:36:03,840
I'll leave work earlier today.

381
00:36:03,840 --> 00:36:07,000
Tell him we can have dinner together.

382
00:36:07,000 --> 00:36:08,039
Okay.

383
00:36:19,920 --> 00:36:22,119
- Mr. Hua.
- Chu San, let's work out together.

384
00:36:22,119 --> 00:36:23,480
We can work out next time.

385
00:36:23,480 --> 00:36:25,719
Chu San, you're back so early today.

386
00:36:25,719 --> 00:36:27,719
What's making you so happy?

387
00:36:27,719 --> 00:36:28,880
Dad.

388
00:36:28,880 --> 00:36:30,160
Liu Yi.

389
00:36:32,800 --> 00:36:33,840
Dad.

390
00:36:33,840 --> 00:36:35,000
Liu Yi.

391
00:36:35,000 --> 00:36:36,159
I brought you some of Yuan Ji's chicken feet.

392
00:36:36,159 --> 00:36:37,800
You're back.

393
00:36:41,119 --> 00:36:43,840
Dad, where is Liu Yi?

394
00:36:43,840 --> 00:36:45,480
He came for acupuncture
in the afternoon and left.

395
00:36:45,480 --> 00:36:47,280
He said he was busy with something.

396
00:37:13,880 --> 00:37:18,512
Mr. Xia, Chu San said he wants you
to stay for dinner tonight.

397
00:37:19,719 --> 00:37:23,159
Recently, he's been eating out a lot

398
00:37:23,159 --> 00:37:25,280
and often doesn't come back at night.

399
00:37:26,079 --> 00:37:29,839
Fei and I both think he's in love.

400
00:37:30,800 --> 00:37:32,160
Don't move.

401
00:37:34,199 --> 00:37:36,280
It's fine.

402
00:37:38,000 --> 00:37:42,239
I don't know what kind of girl he likes.

403
00:37:42,239 --> 00:37:43,280
That kid...

404
00:37:43,280 --> 00:37:44,840
Don't be fooled by his soft personality.

405
00:37:44,840 --> 00:37:46,880
Actually, he's very principled.

406
00:37:46,880 --> 00:37:49,760
He probably doesn't like aggressive girls.

407
00:37:53,159 --> 00:37:57,359
He probably likes fair and demure girls.

408
00:38:00,519 --> 00:38:03,199
But I'm not worried.

409
00:38:03,199 --> 00:38:04,679
This kid has good taste.

410
00:38:04,679 --> 00:38:08,160
He never associates with bad people.

411
00:38:09,000 --> 00:38:10,000
It'll be a little painful.

412
00:38:10,000 --> 00:38:11,159
Hold on, hold on.

413
00:38:11,159 --> 00:38:12,320
It hurts a little.

414
00:38:12,320 --> 00:38:15,039
By the way, what would you like to eat today?

415
00:38:15,039 --> 00:38:16,359
I'll make it for you.

416
00:38:19,119 --> 00:38:22,320
Mr. He, I won't eat here today.

417
00:38:22,320 --> 00:38:23,559
I have things to do, so I have to leave.

418
00:38:23,559 --> 00:38:25,039
Bye.

419
00:38:25,039 --> 00:38:26,600
- You're really busy?
- Bye!

420
00:38:29,239 --> 00:38:31,039
I haven't taken the needle out yet.

421
00:38:38,800 --> 00:38:40,839
This kid, He Chu San.

422
00:38:41,559 --> 00:38:43,640
What's wrong with him?

423
00:38:44,480 --> 00:38:46,199
He's always causing trouble for me.

424
00:38:46,199 --> 00:38:49,200
I treated him as a brother,
but what did he take me for?

425
00:38:57,719 --> 00:38:58,880
Xia Liu Yi.

426
00:38:58,880 --> 00:39:00,160
It's me.

427
00:39:01,679 --> 00:39:03,320
He Chu San.

428
00:39:03,320 --> 00:39:04,599
How did you make the call?

429
00:39:04,599 --> 00:39:06,280
I'm at a public phone booth.

430
00:39:06,920 --> 00:39:08,480
I got paid today.

431
00:39:08,480 --> 00:39:10,080
I bought you some food.

432
00:39:12,480 --> 00:39:13,559
I'm out of town.

433
00:39:13,559 --> 00:39:15,559
I'm busy.

434
00:39:15,559 --> 00:39:17,919
But I see that your light is still on.

435
00:39:20,272 --> 00:39:22,695
[Xiaoqi Trading]
